</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Cufflinks which were among items stolen from Prince Charles's private
apartments in St James's Palace two weeks ago were handed to police by a
London businessman. Police said they were taking no action against the man
and that inquiries were continuing as to how the cufflinks came into his
possession.
