<HEADLINE>
FT  10 MAR 94 / UK Company News: Wates proposes share buy-in
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Wates City of London Properties said it will propose a resolution at the AGM
on May 4 allowing it to buy up to 23.1m of its ordinary shares in the
market.
Wates proposes to buy the shares at a price not exceeding 250p and not less
than 25p apiece.
