FT  10 MAR 94 / UK Company News: Cupid confirms Richard Shaw resignation
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Cupid, the bridal wear manufacturer, yesterday confirmed that its chief
executive, Mr Richard Shaw, would resign with immediate effect.
The company said its objectives had changed since Mr Shaw was appointed to
direct an acquisition programme last year. 'Mr Shaw's skills are not
appropriate for the company's immediate management requirements,' Cupid
said.
